===Noun===
'''vacuum cleaner''' (''plural'' '''vacuum cleaners''')

#A domestic or industrial mobile machine for cleaning floors and similar surfaces, that draws dust, etc., into a container (often a bag) by the suction created by an electric motor driving a fan.

